  "prompt": "Which are the best IELTS coaching institutes in Delhi?",
  "response": "Here are some highly regarded **IELTS coaching institutes in Delhi** based on their reputation, success rates, and student feedback:\n\n### 1. **IELTS Ninja**\n   - Known for its personalized coaching, online and offline classes, and affordable packages.\n   - Offers comprehensive study material and mock tests.\n\n### 2. **British Council**\n   - A trusted name for IELTS coaching and test preparation.\n   - Provides expert trainers, practice tests, and online resources.\n   - Located in Connaught Place, Delhi.\n\n### 3. **IELTS Coaching in Delhi by Jamboree Education**\n   - Focuses on personalized attention and structured learning.\n   - Offers both classroom and online programs.\n\n### 4. **Manya - The Princeton Review**\n   - Known for its experienced faculty and quality study material.\n   - Provides flexible schedules and mock tests.\n\n### 5. **IELTS Delhi**\n   - Offers tailored coaching programs for all sections of the IELTS exam.\n   - Known for its high success rate and affordable fees.\n\n### 6. **Edwise International**\n   - Provides IELTS coaching as well as overseas education counseling.\n   - Offers comprehensive training and practice sessions.\n\n### 7. **Kanan International**\n   - Known for its result-oriented approach and experienced trainers.\n   - Offers both online and offline coaching.\n\n### 8. **Cambridge English Academy (CEA)**\n   - Focuses on intensive training and mock tests.\n   - Known for its affordable fees and experienced faculty.\n\n### 9. **Touchstone Educationals**\n   - Offers specialized IELTS preparation programs.\n   - Known for its structured curriculum and experienced trainers.\n\n### 10. **Grad-Dreams**\n   - Provides IELTS coaching, study material, and mock tests.\n   - Offers both online and offline classes.\n\n### Tips for Choosing the Best Institute:\n- Check the success rate and reviews of the institute.\n- Look for experienced and certified trainers.\n- Ensure they provide ample practice tests and study material.\n- Compare fees and course duration.\n- Opt for institutes offering flexible schedules (online or offline) if needed.\n\nBefore enrolling, consider attending a demo class or speaking to past students to make an informed decision.",
